1. *Osuđen* je na kaznu zatvora od pet godina. (He was *sentenced* to five years in prison.)
2. Sudija je *osudio* optuženog na doživotni zatvor. (The judge *convicted* the defendant to life imprisonment.)
3. Advokat je rekao da je njegov klijent *neosuđen* i nevin. (The lawyer said that his client was *unconvicted* and innocent.)
4. Ona je *osudila* njegov postupak kao neprihvatljiv. (She *condemned* his behavior as unacceptable.)
5. *Osuđeni* je izjavio da će se žaliti na presudu. (The *convict* stated that he would appeal the verdict.)
6. Novinar je *osudio* vladu zbog korupcije. (The journalist *criticized* the government for corruption.)
7. *Osuđeni* je pobjegao iz zatvora nakon samo nekoliko dana. (The *prisoner* escaped from prison after just a few days.)
8. Sudija je *oslobodio optuženog* zbog nedostatka dokaza. (The judge *acquitted the defendant* due to lack of evidence.)
9. Nakon što su ga *osudili* za krađu, morao je platiti novčanu kaznu. (After being *convicted* of theft, he had to pay a fine.)
10. *Osuda* je donesena nakon dugog suđenja. (The *sentence* was handed down after a long trial.)